section.hero.is-light
  .hero-body
    .container
      #causes
        h3.title.is-spaced My cause areas
        p.subtitle These are my priorities for how I am making an impact on the world.
        .carousel data-flickity='{ "cellAlign": "left" }' style='margin: 0 -1rem 3rem'
          - 6.times do
            .carousel-cell style='width: 25rem; padding: 1rem; max-width: 100%'
              .card
                .card-content
                  p.subtitle Global Poverty Eradication
                  p
                    ' Makes direct cash transfers to people living below the poverty line in Kenya, Uganda and Rwanda.
                    | Independently verified studies have demonstrated that this is amongst the most efficient ways to improve lives and lift families out of extreme poverty.
        p.has-text-centered: small Donational helps you find cause areas that you are passionate about, creating a portfolio of high impact charities

section.hero
  .hero-body
    .container
      #charities
        h3.title Charities in my portfolio
        p.subtitle
          ' All of the charities in my portfolio make real impact in cause areas that are important to me.
        .carousel data-flickity='{ "cellAlign": "left" }' style='margin: 0 -1rem 3rem'
          - 6.times do
            .carousel-cell style='width: 25rem; padding: 1rem; max-width: 100%'
              .card
                .card-content
                  p.subtitle GiveDirectly
                  p
                    ' GiveDirectly makes direct cash transfers to people living below the poverty line in Kenya, Uganda and Rwanda.
                    | Independently verified studies have demonstrated that this is amongst the most efficient ways to improve lives and lift families out of extreme poverty.
